{"text_id":198163,"tokens":["This"," paper"," addresses"," the"," problem"," of"," capturing"," the"," co","-","evolution"," of"," user"," and"," item"," features"," in"," recomm","ender"," systems","."," The"," strength"," of"," the"," paper"," is"," that"," it"," proposes"," a"," new"," model"," that"," combines"," recurrent"," neural"," networks"," (","RNN","s",")"," with"," a"," multi","-","dimensional"," point"," process"," model"," to"," learn"," nonlinear"," representations"," of"," user"," and"," item"," embeddings"," that"," take"," into"," account"," mutual"," influence"," between"," user"," and"," item"," features",","," and"," the"," feature"," evolution"," over"," time","."," The"," proposed"," model"," is"," evaluated"," on"," real","-","world"," datasets"," and"," compared"," to"," state","-","of","-","the","-","art"," methods",","," where"," the"," results"," demonstrate"," significant"," improvements"," in"," user"," behavior"," prediction","."," ","\n","However",","," there"," are"," some"," weaknesses"," in"," the"," paper","."," First",","," the"," experimental"," results"," are"," not"," well","-","controlled","."," For"," example",","," the"," base","lines"," used"," in"," the"," experiments"," are"," not"," clearly"," defined",","," and"," it"," is"," not"," clear"," how"," the"," proposed"," method"," compares"," to"," other"," state","-","of","-","the","-","art"," methods","."," Second",","," the"," evaluation"," metrics"," used"," in"," the"," experiments"," are"," not"," the"," most"," appropriate"," for"," evaluating"," recommendation"," systems","."," Finally",","," the"," authors"," do"," not"," discuss"," the"," limitations"," of"," their"," approach"," or"," how"," it"," could"," be"," improved"," in"," the"," future","."],"sub_source":"peerread","model":"cohere","label":1}